snippet.title: Cereal Killer (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Follow Milton, a farmer who witnesses strange events on his farm until he realizes that his cereal plantation is more alive than it should be..

Note: All themes and characters covered in this game are from a fictional universe and do not portray reality!
